    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players take command of aliens, robots and humans using their unique playstyles to destroy the opponent's energy core. Discover synergy between the cards to craft your combos. Players will face off against the enemy AI in singleplayer or other players in multiplayer mode. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204750/extras/4c1797dcec4f1cb9bbbf201bf3a3c252.poster.avif?t=1740011964\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204750/extras/4c1797dcec4f1cb9bbbf201bf3a3c252.webm?t=1740011964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204750/extras/4c1797dcec4f1cb9bbbf201bf3a3c252.mp4?t=1740011964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mechanics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 3 main races.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Aliens: Balanced offense and defense, excelling in neither. Effects allow for a board control based approach.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Robots: Typically boast higher defense. Effects have a focus on destruction and sustainability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Humans: Higher attack power but low defense. Their effects boost each other, call for reinforcements and can equip weapons to become even stronger. </p></li></ul>",
